import numpy as np
import tensorflow as tf
import pathlib
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from tensorflow import keras
import os
import shutil
from tensorflow.keras import layers
from tensorflow.keras.preprocessing.image import ImageDataGenerator
from tensorflow.keras.applications import ResNet50
from sklearn.metrics import (
    classification_report,
    confusion_matrix,
    precision_recall_curve,
    auc,
)
from keras.utils import to_categorical


trainDataDir = pathlib.Path("/home/justin/Documents/AI_ML/CSCN8010-lab-submissions/students_submissions/8786567/archivebird/train")
testDataDir = pathlib.Path("/home/justin/Documents/AI_ML/CSCN8010-lab-submissions/students_submissions/8786567/archivebird/test")
validDataDir = pathlib.Path("/home/justin/Documents/AI_ML/CSCN8010-lab-submissions/students_submissions/8786567/archivebird/valid")


dataAugmentation = ImageDataGenerator(
    rotation_range=30,
    shear_range=0.2,
    zoom_range=0.2,
    horizontal_flip=True,
)

numClasses = 3


trainClassCounts = {classLabel: len(os.listdir(os.path.join(trainDataDir, classLabel)))
                      for classLabel in os.listdir(trainDataDir)}

topClasses = [classLabel for classLabel, count in sorted(trainClassCounts.items(), key=lambda x: x[1], reverse=True)[:3]]
print("Top 3 most frequent classes from training data:", topClasses)


for currDir in [trainDataDir, testDataDir, validDataDir]:
    for classLabel in os.listdir(currDir):
        if classLabel not in topClasses:
            pathToRemove = os.path.join(currDir, classLabel)
            if os.path.isdir(pathToRemove):
                shutil.rmtree(pathToRemove)

dataGenerator = ImageDataGenerator(
    rotation_range=20,
    shear_range=0.2,
    zoom_range=0.1,
    horizontal_flip=True,
)

dataTrain = dataGenerator.flow_from_directory(
    trainDataDir, target_size=(180, 180), batch_size=32, class_mode="categorical"
)

dataTest = dataGenerator.flow_from_directory(
    testDataDir, target_size=(180, 180), batch_size=32, class_mode="categorical"
)

dataValid = dataGenerator.flow_from_directory(
    validDataDir, target_size=(180, 180), batch_size=32, class_mode="categorical"
)


baseModel = ResNet50(weights="imagenet", include_top=False, input_shape=(180, 180, 3))
baseModel.trainable = False
baseModel.summary()

x = baseModel.output
x = layers.Flatten()(x)
x = layers.Dense(256)(x)
x = layers.Dropout(0.5)(x)
outputs = layers.Dense(numClasses, activation="softmax")(x)
model = keras.Model(baseModel.input, outputs)

model.summary()


model.compile(
    optimizer=keras.optimizers.Adam(learning_rate=1e-5),
    loss="categorical_crossentropy",
    metrics=["accuracy"],
)
callbacks = [
    keras.callbacks.ModelCheckpoint(
        filepath="./log/models/fine_tuning.keras",
        save_best_only=True,
        monitor="val_loss",
    )
]
history = model.fit(
    dataTrain, epochs=5, validation_data=dataValid, callbacks=callbacks
)

acc = history.history["accuracy"]
valAcc = history.history["val_accuracy"]
loss = history.history["loss"]
valLoss = history.history["val_loss"]
epochs = range(1, len(acc) + 1)

plt.plot(epochs, acc, "bo", label="Training accuracy")
plt.plot(epochs, valAcc, "b", label="Validation accuracy")
plt.title("Training & validation accuracy")
plt.legend()
plt.figure()
plt.plot(epochs, loss, "bo", label="Training loss")
plt.plot(epochs, valLoss, "b", label="Validation loss")
plt.title("Training & validation loss")
plt.legend()
plt.show()


testLoss, testAcc = model.evaluate(dataTest)
print(f"Test accuracy: {testAcc:.3f}")


yTrue = dataTest.classes
yPredict = model.predict(dataTest)
yPred = np.argmax(yPredict, axis=1)

print("Confusion Matrix")
print(confusion_matrix(yTrue, yPred))
print("Report")
print(
    classification_report(yTrue, yPred, target_names=dataTest.class_indices.keys()),
)


yTrueEnc = to_categorical(yTrue)


labels = {v: k for k, v in dataTest.class_indices.items()}

for i in range(numClasses):
    actual = yTrueEnc[:, i]
    predictions = yPredict[:, i]
    precision, recall, _ = precision_recall_curve(actual, predictions)
    label = f"[{labels[i]}] AUC = {auc(recall, precision):.2f}"
    plt.plot(
        recall,
        precision,
        lw=2,
        label=label,
    )

plt.xlabel("Recall")
plt.ylabel("Precision")
plt.legend()
plt.show()


misclassifiedIndices = np.where(yPred != yTrue)[0]

for i in misclassifiedIndices[:5]:
 
    batchIndex = i // dataTest.batch_size
    batch, _ = dataTest[batchIndex]
    imageIndexInsideBatch = i % dataTest.batch_size
    img = batch[imageIndexInsideBatch]

    
    actualLabel = labels[yTrue[i]]
    predictedLabel = labels[yPred[i]]

    
    plt.imshow(img.astype("uint8"))
    plt.title(f"Actual: {actualLabel}, Predicted: {predictedLabel}")
    plt.axis("off")
    plt.show()
